    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor shortfalls at MRL 5, the assessment package is accepted for submission to the regulatory dossier as a documented evidence base. The identified gaps are recorded as open action items requiring resolution prior to final device clearance. The Monte Carlo UQ results bound overall prediction uncertainty at the system level, providing sufficient basis for conditional acceptance pending gap closure.",
